The following [Phrase](phrase-ref) searches  *all fields*  for the
string `red`.

```javascript
db.cars.aggregate([
  {
    "$search": {
      "phrase": {
        "path": { "wildcard": "*" },
        "query": "red"
      }
    }
  }
])
```

The query returns the following results:

```json
