The following [text](text-ref) searches the fields nested
within the `warehouse` field for the string `red`.

```javascript
db.cars.aggregate([
  {
    "$search": {
      "text": {
        "path": { "wildcard": "warehouse.*" },
        "query": "red"
      }
    }
  }
])
```

